ModalDoubleCheckerComponent.help1-a: If the delete button is disabled, it means that the flag has at least one active kanban column.
ModalDoubleCheckerComponent.help1-b: To remove 'Nets' from the flag, you need to go to 'Open Kanban' and delete the social medias or kanban columns.
ModalDoubleCheckerComponent.help1-c: After doing this, the delete button will be enabled.
